    </p>

    <p>Note that this Policy does not govern the use of any third-party websites or applications, including without limitation third-party websites or applications that provide access to The Shoplift or to data or content owned or licensed by Shoplift Inc. Please consult the privacy policy of any website or application, and familiarize yourself with its terms, before you begin using it.</p>

