    </p>

    <p><br />
    </p>

    <ol > <li>We primarily use the information we collect about you to improve the quality of the Services and to customize your experience and the experience of other users using the Services. This includes Personal Information (for instance, we use your name and photo to showcase the items you share when we show them to other users) and non-identifying information (for instance, we use what we know about your taste to show you items and users we believe will be relevant to you).</li>
    </ol><p><br />
    </p>

    <ol > <li>We use the information we collect about you, including Personal Information, for a variety of administrative purposes – for example, to administer your account; to provide you with customer support; to respond to your requests; to resolve disputes and/or troubleshoot problems; to verify your compliance with our <a href='/terms_of_service'>Terms of Use</a>; and to communicate with you about the Services.</li>
