    </ol><p><br />
    </p>

    <ol > <li>We may also share some of the information we collect about you privately, with individual users of the Services, in order to improve the experience for you, those individual users, or all users. For instance, if we believe that another user is likely to share or appreciate your taste, we may recommend that he or she follow you, and we may include your name and profile on a customized screen we show that user.</li>
    </ol><p><br />
